
OVERVIEW :
The Flappy Bird Game is a Java application that replicates the popular mobile game with smooth animations and responsive user input handling.
Developed using Java Swing, this game features intuitive controls, engaging gameplay, and a scoring system to track high scores. 
The game offers an enjoyable experience with a user-friendly interface and simple mechanics.


FILES:
FlappyBirdGame.java: Contains the FlappyBirdGame class, which extends JPanel and implements ActionListener and KeyListener.
This class handles the game mechanics, rendering, and user input.
